data.title: Maurice Cloche
data.meta_description: Maurice Cloche. Director: L'invité de la onzième heure. Maurice Cloche was born on 17 June 1907 in Commercy, Meuse, France. He was a director and writer, known for L'invité de la onzième heure (1945), Monsieur Vincent (1947) and La cage aux filles (1949). He died on 20 March 1990 in Bordeaux, Gironde, France.
data.text: Maurice Cloche was born on June 17, 1907 in Commercy, Meuse, France. He was a director and writer, known for L'invité de la onzième heure (1945), Monsieur Vincent (1947) and La cage aux filles (1949). He died on March 20, 1990 in Bordeaux, Gironde, France.
